{
  "id": "RAW_38b517",
  "title": "【第 3575 期】解锁 AI 响应中的丰富 UI 组件渲染",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&mid=2651277284&idx=1&sn=c96010fa50abd506a21064e332bbf967",
  "date": "2025-08-25 00:02:00",
  "author": "前端早读课",
  "siteName": "前端早读课",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>\n   <br>\n  </p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b28a6223&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FmeG6Vo0MeviaUkF67icpwXehyWGptKGctCms4lwpAibdHqAZ4J1dpS4hWV36MmHl5Tt8HDJBHIZSePkvwNAibz1ibxA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px !important;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">前言</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">探讨了如何在 AI 响应中整合丰富的 UI 组件，特别是在语言模型（LLM）的文本输出中嵌入 React 组件，以改善传统的以文本为主的 AI 界面。今日前端早读课文章由 @Tim Etler 分享，@飘飘编译。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">译文从这开始～～</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">大语言模型（LLMs）让我们能以比以往更灵活的方式解决一类全新的问题，但由于它们本质上是基于语言的模型，主要输出还是文本，这也导致很多基于 AI 的界面变得 “文字堆砌”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">作为一个一直使用 Web 技术创造体验的人，我对大量 UI 被纯文字替代并不满意。在 Vetted，我们正在构建一个购物研究助手，而购物本身就是一个高度依赖视觉和界面的场景。商品需要展示图片，界面需要提供结构化数据，帮助用户在商品之间导航和比较。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&amp;mid=2651277249&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=3785b80105ed8f47ea54de68a1fec60a&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"【早阅】OpenAI工程师：沟通是编程的核心价值\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">【早阅】OpenAI工程师：沟通是编程的核心价值</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">这些年来，我们一直在尝试把更丰富的 UI 组件融入到 LLM 的回答中。我们的做法是：在文本输出中补充结构化的商品数据，这些数据可以被渲染为商品卡片或研究组件。但问题是，这些组件往往和核心的文字回答割裂开来，这让体验并不理想。所以，我开始探索一种方法，让 LLM 的输出能直接在 Markdown 结果中嵌入 UI 组件。</span></p>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">MDX 增强的动态 Markdown</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">推荐看看 react-markdown-with-mdx。它是对&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">react-markdown</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;的一个高阶组件（HOC）封装，增强了 Markdown 的处理能力，使其支持 JSX 组件标签。你可以在其中注册白名单的 React 组件，确保只有一部分经过允许的 JSX 标签可以被渲染。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个库还带有一个可选的验证辅助函数&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">mdxComponent</span></code><span leaf=\"\">，它可以结合 zod 校验器来验证 JSX 属性。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&amp;mid=2651247047&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b22731dce3927c0dc0881c99d9fa7c34&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"【第2308期】@Amour1688：探索Vue3中的JSX\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">【第2308期】@Amour1688：探索Vue3中的JSX</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">这样，你就能在调用 LLM 时生成可安全使用的 JSX 标签，并且轻松无缝地集成到界面中。在 Vetted 的原型 UI 中，它的效果大概是这样的：</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">代码示例如下：</span></p>\n  <pre tabindex=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:10px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:3px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;widows:2;font:400 13.6px / 1.45 Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;text-align:start;\"><code style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:12px;line-height:inherit;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:5px;overflow:auto;word-break:normal;font-family:Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;import ReactMarkdown from \"react-markdown\"</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;import { withMdx, mdxComponent, type MdxComponents} from \"react-markdown-with-mdx\"</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;const MdxReactMarkdown = withMdx(ReactMarkdown)</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;interface MdxMarkdownRendererProps {</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;markdown: string</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;}</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;const MdxMarkdownRenderer: React.FC&lt;MdxMarkdownRendererProps&gt; = ({</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;markdown,</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;}) =&gt; {</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;return (</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;MdxReactMarkdown components={components}&gt;</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;{markdown}</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;/MdxReactMarkdown&gt;</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;)</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;}</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;const components: MdxComponents = {</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;\"card-carousel\": mdxComponent(</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;MdxCardCarousel,</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;z.object({ children: z.any() })</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;),</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;\"editorial-card\": mdxComponent(</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;MdxEditorialCard,</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;z.object({</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;id: z.string(),</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;award: z.string().optional(),</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;rating: z.string().optional(),</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;ranking: z.string().optional(),</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;children: z.any()</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;})</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;),</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;\"product-card\": mdxComponent(</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;MdxProductCard,</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;z.object({ name: z.string() })</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;)</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;}</span></code></pre>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">与 MCP-UI 这类项目不同，这些组件并不是通过 iframe 外部加载，也不需要&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">window.postMessage</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;来集成，更不是和主回答分离的 “额外消息”。相反，这些组件会被直接解析成框架原生的 React 组件，并与 LLM 生成的正文紧密结合。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">换句话说，它让 React 及其他 JSX 框架中的 Markdown，拥有类似 HTML 组件扩展的能力，你几乎可以嵌入任何你想象得到的 UI 组件！</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&amp;mid=2651262450&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=69176ec27aedbc5abaa984485e8f6309&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"【第2935期】10分钟打造基于ChatGPT的Markdown智能文档\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">【第2935期】10分钟打造基于ChatGPT的Markdown智能文档</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了支持视频中展示的流式响应，我们还必须解决 HTML 标签树的平衡问题：需要在输出时截断不完整的标签，确保传给 MDX 解析器的始终是有效的 HTML，防止半截标签被提前渲染。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">为此，我还写了一个工具 html-balancer-stream，它可以自动补全和闭合未完成的标签，或者在准备好之前将其剔除，以便真正实现流式渲染。该工具同时提供流式和非流式 API。</span></p>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">工作原理：用 MDX 为 AI Markdown 响应 “加速”</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">最初我尝试的原型方案是直接使用 HTML 组件。这种方式确实能跑通：因为 HTML 组件会直接注册到浏览器的 DOM，所以自定义 HTML 组件可以作为标签字符串注入到&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">innerHTML</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;中，而不需要额外的渲染逻辑。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">不过，这种做法虽然适合原型验证，但我并不满意。若在生产环境使用 HTML 注入，会带来严重的安全风险，而且还可能对我们的渲染框架产生副作用。我希望能找到一种既安全，又能与 React（我们在 Vetted 使用的渲染框架）紧密结合的方式来实现这一点。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&amp;mid=2651277236&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=27a9d68a574ac89c711e85c432a93629&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"【第3570期】LLM 和 ChatGPT：文本提示与 JSON 提示的对比\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">【第3570期】LLM 和 ChatGPT：文本提示与 JSON 提示的对比</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 Markdown 渲染方面，我们已经在用 react-markdown 把 LLM 生成的 Markdown 转成 React 组件。Markdown 本身是支持原始 HTML 的，但 react-markdown 出于安全考虑并不支持，它会把 HTML 标签转义成纯文本字符串 —— 因为允许在动态 Markdown 内容中嵌入任意 HTML 是极其危险的。</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\">另外，我的目标也不是单纯支持 HTML 或 HTML 组件，而是要让 Markdown 能够以框架原生的方式支持 React 组件。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">为此，我开始深入研究 react-markdown 的内部原理。它基于 unified 项目 —— 一个用来解析和转换语法树的框架和社区生态，可以组合并转换不同语言。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">实际上，react-markdown 只是 unified 的一个 “轻量封装”，流程大致是：先用 remark（Markdown 处理器）把 Markdown 转成 mdast（Markdown AST），然后通过 remark-rehype 转换为 hast（HTML AST），最后再用 hast-util-to-jsx-runtime 安全地把 hast AST 转换为 JSX 组件，供 React（或其他基于 JSX 的框架）渲染。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">理解了这些之后，我觉得最佳方案就是扩展 remark 的解析能力，让它支持 JSX。幸运的是，react-markdown 的 README 里也提到过这一点，并推荐开发者使用 MDX—— 它允许你在 Markdown 中直接写 JSX 语法！看起来问题解决了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">不过事情并没有这么简单。MDX 功能非常强大，不仅支持在 Markdown 中插入静态 JSX 组件，还支持完整的 JSX 语法，包括&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">import</span></code><span leaf=\"\">、</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">export</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;以及动态 JavaScript 表达式。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">这就带来一个大问题：如果直接把 MDX 用在 LLM 动态输出中，安全风险将会非常大 —— 等于又回到了原点。MDX 作者本身也很清楚这一点，所以 MDX 项目的定位并不是 “运行时渲染”，而是 “编译时渲染”，主要用于构建静态站点的安全场景。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">值得庆幸的是，MDX 也是基于 unified 项目<a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&amp;mid=2651276606&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=9428064706c9d9b0f531ce5d0d836f65&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"构建\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">构建</a>的，而 unified 的解析与转换管道高度灵活和模块化。这意味着虽然我不能直接拿 MDX 开箱即用，但我可以利用 remark-mdx 解析器生成 MDX AST，再自己构建一个解析流程，只保留我需要的那部分功能：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">让 Markdown 支持静态 JSX 组件，并允许 LLM 输出的 Markdown 中包含 JSX 组件标签，而这些标签可以安全地转换成 React 的运行时组件。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">为此，我需要写几个新库：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;padding-left:2em;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;list-style-type: disc;\">\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">remark-mdx：它会在 remark 的 mdast 语法树中检测到 JSX 标签，并解析成 MDX AST，把节点插入到语法树中。这样语法树中同时包含 Markdown 节点和 JSX 节点。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0.25em;list-style-type: disc;\">\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">接下来，我只需要剔除 MDX 的动态语法，保留静态语法即可。为此我写了 rehype-mdx-elements，它把静态 JSX 标签转换成 hast AST 的 HTML 元素。然后再由 hast-util-to-jsx-runtime 把它们转换成真正的 JSX 组件调用。由于 hast-util-to-jsx-runtime 需要开发者显式传入允许使用的组件，这就确保了整个流程不会意外渲染任何任意 HTML。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0.25em;list-style-type: disc;\">\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">另外，我还写了 remark-unravel-mdx，它的作用是去掉包裹在 MDX 节点外层的多余&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&lt;p&gt;</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;标签，让组件树更干净（MDX 本身内部也会做类似处理）。</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">最后，把这些组合在一起，就形成了 react-markdown-with-mdx 的处理管道，它实现了 MDX → JSX 运行时组件的转换，也就是我们在演示中看到的效果。</span></p>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">生成 LLM JSX 输出</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">要让 AI 生成的内容与 JSX 组件结合，其实很简单：你只需要在提示词里告诉 LLM 组件的标签、属性结构，以及允许的子元素，并给出一些使用示例。由于 JSX 标签和 XML 在语法上几乎一致，而 LLM 在 XML 上训练得很充分，所以它在生成静态 JSX 标签方面表现得非常好。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&amp;mid=2651277174&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=2305e2835aafc1e0b1e293dc62393c99&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"【第3566期】UI 的未来：从命令行到对话式 AI\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">【第3566期】UI 的未来：从命令行到对话式 AI</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">不过，JSX 标签和展示属性一旦涉及复杂数据关系，很容易变得耦合度高、难以控制。我的建议是：让 LLM 生成的属性保持尽可能简单和精简。我们的做法是：只让 LLM 输出本地的引用 ID 字符串，再由外层包装组件去共享上下文或数据存储中查找这些 ID，填充更复杂的 props 来驱动展示组件。这样，LLM 只需要生成一些上下文相关的衍生数据，比如从研究资料中提取出来的简短文字。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">由于输出的只是 JSX 标签，它们能与现有组件做到 一一对应，这意味着你现有的文档和 schema 定义既能在代码库里用，也能放到提示词里用，从而保持定义和版本的一致性。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">我一直觉得 LLM 的输出和前端渲染框架之间应该有更紧密的连接，而我也很期待 react-markdown-with-mdx 能真正弥补这个缺口！</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:0px !important;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">关于本文</span></span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">译者：@飘飘</span></span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">作者：@Tim Etler</span></span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">原文：<a href=\"https://www.timetler.com/2025/08/19/unlocking-rich-ui-components-in-ai/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.timetler.com/2025/08/19/unlocking-rich-ui-components-in-ai/</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章详细阐述了如何通过 MDX 及自定义解析器，将 React UI 组件安全地嵌入到大语言模型（LLM）的 Markdown 响应中，以改善 AI 界面的用户体验。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章详细阐述了如何通过 MDX 及自定义解析器，将 React UI 组件安全地嵌入到大语言模型（LLM）的 Markdown 响应中，以改善 AI 界面的用户体验。",
  "summary": "文章深入探讨了传统大语言模型（LLM）输出以文本为主，导致 AI 应用界面过于“文字堆砌”的问题，尤其在需要丰富视觉和交互的场景（如购物助手）中体验不佳。为解决此痛点，作者提出了一种创新方案：将 React UI 组件安全地嵌入到 LLM 生成的 Markdown 响应中。该方案利用了 MDX 在 Markdown 中支持 JSX 的特性，但为规避 MDX 完整运行时带来的安全风险，作者基于`unified`项目生态，构建了一套自定义解析管道，仅支持静态 JSX 组件的解析与渲染。具体实现包括`remark-mdx`、`rehype-mdx-elements`等库，确保了组件能够以框架原生方式与 LLM 文本紧密结合。在与 LLM 集成时，建议让 LLM 生成简洁的 JSX 标签和引用 ID，由前端包装组件负责数据填充，从而保证了输出的简洁性、安全性和可维护性。文章还提到了`html-balancer-stream`工具用于流式响应中 HTML 标签的平衡处理，旨在弥补 LLM 输出与前端渲染框架之间的鸿沟，提升 AI 应用的交互性和用户体验。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "传统 LLM 文本输出导致 AI 界面文字堆砌，引入 UI 组件可显著改善用户体验。",
      "explanation": "大语言模型主要输出文本，使得 AI 应用界面缺乏视觉和交互丰富性。通过在 LLM 的 Markdown 响应中直接嵌入 React 等 UI 组件，能为购物助手等视觉依赖型应用提供更丰富的交互和结构化数据展示，提升用户体验。"
    },
    {
      "point": "利用 MDX 的 JSX 支持，通过自定义解析器安全地将 React 组件嵌入 Markdown。",
      "explanation": "文章提出基于`unified`生态系统，构建一套安全的解析管道，扩展 Markdown 解析能力以支持静态 JSX 组件渲染，从而规避了完整 MDX 运行时可能带来的安全风险和副作用，实现组件与内容的紧密结合。"
    },
    {
      "point": "LLM 通过生成简单 JSX 标签，配合外层组件进行数据填充，实现组件与内容紧密结合。",
      "explanation": "通过在提示词中明确组件标签和属性结构，引导 LLM 生成简洁的引用 ID，再由前端包装组件根据 ID 从共享上下文或数据存储中填充复杂 props，确保了 LLM 输出的简洁性、安全性和与现有组件的对应关系。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "大语言模型（LLMs）让我们能以比以往更灵活的方式解决一类全新的问题，但由于它们本质上是基于语言的模型，主要输出还是文本，这也导致很多基于 AI 的界面变得 '文字堆砌'。",
    "我开始探索一种方法，让 LLM 的输出能直接在 Markdown 结果中嵌入 UI 组件。",
    "换句话说，它让 React 及其他 JSX 框架中的 Markdown，拥有类似 HTML 组件扩展的能力，你几乎可以嵌入任何你想象得到的 UI 组件！",
    "MDX 功能非常强大，不仅支持在 Markdown 中插入静态 JSX 组件，还支持完整的 JSX 语法，包括 import、export 以及动态 JavaScript 表达式。这就带来一个大问题：如果直接把 MDX 用在 LLM 动态输出中，安全风险将会非常大 ------ 等于又回到了原点。",
    "我一直觉得 LLM 的输出和前端渲染框架之间应该有更紧密的连接，而我也很期待 react-markdown-with-mdx 能真正弥补这个缺口！"
  ],
